01:01.395 --> 01:03.938
Krisinski, L. Fort Sill?

01:04.022 --> 01:07.775
Oh , of course. Larry, look at you .

01:07.860 --> 01:09.569
Yeah, and you .

01:09.653 --> 01:11.446
Still haven't filled out,
You must be a bachelor.

01:11.530 --> 01:13.948
No.

01:14.032 --> 01:15.992
Where are you at?
