01:29.548 --> 01:31.966
Yeah , well-- Look, I should , uh--

01:32.050 --> 01:34.051
Call me. We should catch up.

01:35.554 --> 01:36.679
Absolutely.

01:36.764 --> 01:37.972
Old Dick Whitman .

01:38.056 --> 01:40.433
What are the chances?

02:07.085 --> 02:09.545
Good morning, Hollis.

02:09.630 --> 02:11.964
I mean , it's France,
What do they want with the bomb?

02:12.049 --> 02:13.216
