- Hey.

02:17.095 --> 02:19.680
Here comes Romeo
without his roe, like a dried herring .

02:19.765 --> 02:20.932
Do I seem different?

02:21.016 --> 02:22.558
You do look depleted, Humps.

02:22.643 --> 02:23.559
The wedding was great.

02:23.644 --> 02:25.019
How was the rest of it?

02:25.103 --> 02:26.562
You're talking about my wife here.

02:26.647 --> 02:28.606
Oh, she's already got you there?

02:28.690 --> 02:29.816
Gentlemen never discuss this.

02:29.900 --> 02:31.526
We're talking about you here:

02:31.610 --> 02:34.111
the man who told us
the coat check girl from "2 1 "

02:34.196 --> 02:36.656
had tangerine panties.

02:36.740 --> 02:38.825
Come on, buddy boy, spill.

02:38.909 --> 02:40.952
I don't know.

02:41.036 --> 02:43.162
Something happened in the ceremony.

02:43.247 --> 02:46.999
It's when he said that thing
about being new baptized .

02:47.084 --> 02:49.627
I just felt this calm come over me.

02:49.711 --> 02:52.338
So what you're saying is,
uh, a lot of missionary?

02:58.095 --> 02:59.929
Fine.

03:00.013 --> 03:02.473
So she's laying there, right?

03:02.558 --> 03:04.058
And she kept looking at the maps,

03:04.142 --> 03:07.603
talking about all the things
we were going to do. . .

03:07.688 --> 03:09.272
but we never did .

03:09.356 --> 03:11.274
Ladies Home Journal .
I can get that at Mom's.

03:11.358 --> 03:12.692
Welcome back, Mr. Campbell.

03:12.776 --> 03:14.735
Well, hey, there.

03:14.820 --> 03:17.029
The ring , it's like catnip.

03:17.155 --> 03:21.158
Did you know that 600,000 gallons of water
go over the Falls per second?

03:21.243 --> 03:22.243
Per second!

03:22.327 --> 03:24.078
Oh , look. He's back.

03:24.162 --> 03:25.496
Good morning .

03:25.581 --> 03:28.082
- Congratulations.
- Welcome back.

03:28.166 --> 03:29.792
Thanks, everybody.

03:29.877 --> 03:31.168
When did this place get so friendly?

03:31.253 --> 03:32.420
I guess people missed you .

03:32.504 --> 03:34.338
- Welcome back, M r. Campbell.
- Hildy.

03:39.136 --> 03:42.179
Close the door!

03:43.765 --> 03:46.475
Who put the Chinamen in my office?

03:47.561 --> 03:49.061
Welcome back.

03:56.194 --> 04:00.156
They paid an Oriental family
to be in M r. Campbell's office.

04:00.240 --> 04:02.199
Someone will finally
be working in there.

04:10.500 --> 04:13.753
Mr. Romano, Mr, Kinsey, and Mr. Crane
are here for your meeting .

04:16.214 --> 04:17.673
Do you need a minute?

04:17.758 --> 04:19.175
Doyou need a minute? You must.

04:19.259 --> 04:21.969
You keep moving the Secor laxative
discussion .

04:25.223 --> 04:27.224
See what we did to Campbell's office?

04:28.685 --> 04:30.144
What do we have?

04:31.229 --> 04:34.148
Let me remind you, safe and reliable
would make me doze off

04:34.232 --> 04:37.693
if I wasn't so blighted
by the scourge of constipation .

04:37.778 --> 04:40.571
Well , what can I say? I'm blocked .

04:40.656 --> 04:43.157
I told you he wouldn't
think that was funny.

04:43.241 --> 04:44.367
I got one.

04:44.451 --> 04:47.244
How 'bout "Secor. It's satisfeculant"?

04:47.329 --> 04:49.163
Stay in the art department, Sal .

04:49.247 --> 04:53.167
I'm just saying we can be funny,
like those Volkswagen people.

04:53.251 --> 04:54.543
You see this yet?

04:54.628 --> 04:55.753
I have.

04:55.837 --> 04:57.797
I don't know what I hate about it the most,

04:57.881 --> 04:59.090
the ad or the car.

04:59.174 --> 05:00.424
You know, they did one last year.

05:00.509 --> 05:02.176
Same kind of smirk.
Remember "Think small"?

05:02.260 --> 05:04.345
It was a half-page ad in a full-page buy.

05:04.429 --> 05:05.805
You could barely see the product.

05:05.889 --> 05:07.014
I don't get it.

05:07.099 --> 05:08.557
Elvis just got back from West Germany.

05:08.642 --> 05:10.434
Why not put him in it?

05:10.519 --> 05:11.894
They must be getting results.

05:11.979 --> 05:14.313
They keep going back to the well .

05:14.398 --> 05:16.524
I want the Chinamen
out of the building by lunch .

05:16.608 --> 05:18.192
I'm still waiting on my shirts.

05:19.277 --> 05:21.070
You've seen this?

05:34.710 --> 05:37.294
- I'm back now.
- I see that.

05:38.505 --> 05:40.673
So. . .

05:40.757 --> 05:42.883
I should be on the list for the meeting .

05:42.968 --> 05:44.760
Oh, I just--

05:44.845 --> 05:46.554
I didn't know when
you were coming back.

05:46.638 --> 05:47.805
Right.

05:49.307 --> 05:51.934
Yeah , well, it's today. Here I am .

05:53.311 --> 05:55.688
They're all in there already. You can go in .

06:00.277 --> 06:01.318
Peggy. . .

06:05.782 --> 06:07.575
When I came over that night,

06:07.659 --> 06:09.994
you know, before.

06:10.078 --> 06:11.287
I was there.

06:12.330 --> 06:14.665
You know. . .

06:14.750 --> 06:16.333
