12:51.980 --> 12:53.730
- I'll walk you out.
- I've got it.

12:59.737 --> 13:00.654
Harry.

13:00.738 --> 13:01.947
What?

13:03.575 --> 13:06.118
It was nice
the way you handled that.

13:06.202 --> 13:08.162
