13:08.246 --> 13:09.663
Well , it wasn't a lie.

13:09.747 --> 13:12.124
It was ineptitude
with insufficient cover.

13:13.751 --> 13:16.837
Something about the way
you talk always restores my confidence.

13:16.921 --> 13:18.672
I have a deep voice.

13:18.756 --> 13:20.632
This afternoon, then .

13:20.717 --> 13:22.551
It's a date.

13:25.930 --> 13:27.389
New junior exec.

13:34.772 --> 13:37.691
Changing her store
could take six months--

13:37.775 --> 13:40.152
or a year, if I know what's good for me.

13:40.236 --> 13:42.029
- What was that in there?
- What?

13:42.113 --> 13:44.406
Don and Molly Goldberg ,
Did you see that?

13:44.491 --> 13:45.908
Yeah , I caught it. What's your point?

13:45.992 --> 13:47.868
