Hello, honey.

14:50.974 --> 14:52.849
Dinner? Wow.

14:52.934 --> 14:55.310
What do I want for dinner?

14:55.395 --> 14:57.187
I don't know.

14:57.272 --> 14:59.773
Anything but chicken .

14:59.857 --> 15:01.066
Yes, they missed me.

15:01.150 --> 15:04.778
U h , rib eye in the pan with butter.

15:04.862 --> 15:06.780
Ice cream .

15:06.864 --> 15:08.448
I love you , too.

