picked this place up for a shekel .

16:20.938 --> 16:23.440
Well, it is crowded .

16:23.524 --> 16:25.859
But that might have
something to do with the sale,

16:25.943 --> 16:28.236
which means that, if we're successful,

16:28.321 --> 16:29.863
you're gonna lose
the customers you have

16:29.947 --> 16:31.865
in order to get
the customers you want.

16:31.949 --> 16:33.825
I was gonna start with raising prices.

16:33.910 --> 16:35.786
Can you imagine what my father said?

16:35.870 --> 16:37.621
Well, you do have
to give them something

16:37.705 --> 16:38.955
for their higher dollar count.

16:39.040 --> 16:43.043
It's just awfully hard to define what that is.

16:48.675 --> 16:49.883
How may I help you?

16:49.967 --> 16:52.803
I make them say that.

16:52.887 --> 16:55.263
Carol , can we see this tray right here?

17:03.648 --> 17:05.315
Sea horses,

17:05.400 --> 17:06.608
crowns,

17:06.693 --> 17:07.984
lucky dice.

17:08.986 --> 17:11.113
Medieval knights.

17:21.874 --> 17:23.834
That's better.

17:23.918 --> 17:25.001
Thank you .

